HEADWORD: Uncharitable
<hw>Un*char"i*ta*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not
charitable; contrary to charity; severe in judging; harsh; censorious;
<as>as, <ex>uncharitable</ex> opinions or zeal</as>.</def>
<au>Addison.</au> -- <wordforms><wf>Un*char"i*ta*ble*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos> -- <wf>Un*char"i*ta*bly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncharity</ent>⟦br⟧
